  "text": "The blood flow values of the bone samples determined by simultaneous injection of two FM correlated significantly (r = 0.96, r 2 = 0.92, y = 1.06x + 0.05; fig. 1a ). The slope was close to 1 and the intercept close to 0. The comparison of Bland and Altman [CITATION_1] showed a mean difference of 0.39 B 1.11 ml/min/100 g ( fig. 1b) .",
